Project Title

 Sales Data Dashboard using Excel

Project Objective

The main goal of this project is to analyze sales and profit performance using an interactive Excel dashboard.
It helps users quickly understand:

Which states generate the highest profit
Which cities perform best
Which products are least profitable
Most used shipment mode
Sales trends based on customer segment, category, and ship mode

This dashboard supports business decision-making by turning raw sales data into easy visual insights.

